DroidProfiles
=============

NOTE: This project has not been released due to some issues with playing custom ringtones dynamically.  Until a work around is found, this app will not be released to the public.



This will allow you to make custom profiles for your phone.  BlackBerry phone users should be very familar with this.
You can customize specific profile settings for SMS, MMS, EMAIL, PHONE notifications.

You can specify an active profile and set profiles for specific contacts to override that profile.

Comments and suggestions welcome along with patches.

